    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6">
        <h2>Get the right look and feel.</h2>
        <p>
          Authentic 'astragal' external georgian bars, either ovolo or bevelled bars complimented by a spacer bar framework within the glass unit give the appearance of traditional, individual glass units. Or alternatively standard internal georgian bars in either 18mm or 25mm.
        </p>
        <p>
          The internal georgian bar can be formed to create many styles and decorative shapes.
        </p>
